column2: SELECT p.objid, p.ra, p.dec,p.dered_u,p.dered_g,p.dered_r,p.dered_i,p.dered_z,p.clean,p.flags                 , z.z as photoz,z.zErr as photozErr, s.z_noqso as specz,s.zErr_noqso as speczErr                 , dbo.fPhotoFlagsN(p.flags) as note                 FROM GALAXY as p                 LEFT OUTER JOIN photoz as z ON z.objID = p.objID                 LEFT OUTER JOIN specObjAll as s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID                 , dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#,#) as near                 WHERE p.objID = near.objID AND                  ((flags & #)!=#) AND ((flags & #)=#) AND                  ((flags & #)=#) AND ((flags & #)!=#)
